<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<title>
			Request Password Reset
		</title>
	</head>
	<body>
		<h3>
			Password Reset
		</h3>
		<p>
			Hi
			<b>
				{{firstname}},
			</b>
		</p>
		<p>
			It looks like you requested to reset your password. We recommend you
			choose password that you can remember and difficult to guess.
		</p>
		<p>
			If this was you, Please reset your password by clicking on this link
			<a href="{{link}}">
				Reset Password
			</a>
		</p>
		<p>
			If you did not request for this, simply ignore. Nothing will change in
			your account settings, and your account will remain secure.
		</p>
		<p>
			Kindly note that this link is valid for the next 15 minutes.
		</p>
	</body>
</html>